  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SQR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YOU ARE SQR. PART OF YOU IS MISSING.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3433200/extras/353e28cdd87ca0adf7976f39d7f9a8bb.poster.avif?t=1746795363\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3433200/extras/353e28cdd87ca0adf7976f39d7f9a8bb.webm?t=1746795363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3433200/extras/353e28cdd87ca0adf7976f39d7f9a8bb.mp4?t=1746795363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SQR is a challenging, fast thinking puzzle game, wearing a deceptively simple coat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SQR you must use a unique colour swapping mechanic to navigate and complete over 90 levels, and overcome an increasingly complex array of colour themed obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIND WHAT IS MISSING.<br>BLEND IN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SQR Features Red-Green Color Blind support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SQR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YOU ARE SQR. PART OF YOU IS MISSING.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3433200/extras/353e28cdd87ca0adf7976f39d7f9a8bb.poster.avif?t=1746795363\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3433200/extras/353e28cdd87ca0adf7976f39d7f9a8bb.webm?t=1746795363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3433200/extras/353e28cdd87ca0adf7976f39d7f9a8bb.mp4?t=1746795363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SQR is a challenging, fast thinking puzzle game, wearing a deceptively simple coat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SQR you must use a unique colour swapping mechanic to navigate and complete over 90 levels, and overcome an increasingly complex array of colour themed obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIND WHAT IS MISSING.<br>BLEND IN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SQR Features Red-Green Color Blind support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
